  "title": "Light Blue Color Fix",
  "description": "This texture pack fixes wrong light blue glass, glass pane and dye color since 1.12.",
  "body": "## What is this texture pack?\nThis texture pack fixes wrong light blue glass and light blue dye textures since 1.12. In 1.12 \"World of Color Update\" dye colors changed. For example, wools. But the light blue wool didn't match the color of the light blue glass and dye. Years later, in version 25w31a, which is a snapshot of 1.21.9, the texture of the dyes was updated, but the incorrect color of the light blue dye was not fixed. This texture pack fixes this incorrect color.\n\n## How is the light blue wool color previously?\nBefore version 1.12, light blue wool looked like this:\n\n![Light Blue Wool from 1.2.4](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/67385f21c234845f20f052487e92609a9d72d3a6.png)\n\nThe light blue glass and dye basically took on the color of this shade. This has not been changed from its state in 1.12.",
